  "title": "Part Time Admin",
  "description": "<h2>📌 Part-Time Admin Assistant (Tuition Centre)</h2><p>We are looking for a <strong>responsible and detail-oriented Part-Time Admin Assistant</strong> to support our daily operations at our tuition centre. If you enjoy working in an educational environment and are good at organisation and communication, we’d love to have you on board!</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Handle tuition enquiries (WhatsApp, calls, walk-ins)</p></li><li><p>Collect and record payments accurately</p></li><li><p>Photocopy, scan, and file documents</p></li><li><p>Coordinate class schedules between tutors, parents, and students</p></li><li><p>Maintain basic administrative records</p></li><li><p>Perform other ad-hoc administrative duties as required</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Responsible, organised, and able to multitask</p></li><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Basic computer skills (Word, Excel, WhatsApp, email)</p></li><li><p>Prior admin or customer service experience is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and follow instructions well</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Working Hours:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Weekday: 1.00pm to 9.30pm, Weekend: 9.00am to 7.30pm</p></li><li><p>Working days to be discussed</p></li></ul><h3><strong></strong></h3><h3><strong>Work Place:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Upper Serangoon View</p></li></ul>",
